## Resolution Prompt Format

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────┐
│  [NAME]                             │
│  DENIED — AWAITING ASSIGNMENT       │
│                                     │
│  ▸ SEND                             │
│    Route to another station.        │
│    Opens new path on map.           │
│                                     │
│  ▸ FIX                              │
│    Modify and requeue.              │
│    They come back changed.          │
│                                     │
│  ▸ PASS                             │
│    Send to higher authority.        │
│    You won't see what happens.      │
│                                     │
│  ▸ HOLD                             │
│    Store indefinitely.              │
│    Frozen. Not gone.                │
│                                     │
│  ▸ RELEASE                          │
│    Let go. Off-grid.                │
│    They don't come back.            │
│                                     │
└─────────────────────────────────────┘
```

