## Directive Display Format

Simple:
```
DENY: WARRANTS
```

With exception:
```
DENY: ENGINEERS
EXCEPT: HUMANS
```

Stacked:
```
DENY: REPLICANTS
EXCEPT: VIP
EXCEPT: MEDICAL
```

