## AMBER Messages

Corporate. Hollow. Bureaucratic. Doesn't acknowledge deaths.

**Examples:**
```
"SHIFT COMPLETE. PROCESSING EFFICIENCY: ACCEPTABLE. GOOD WORK, OPERATOR."
```

```
"3 SUBJECTS PROCESSED. THROUGHPUT WITHIN PARAMETERS. AMBER THANKS YOU."
```

```
"SHIFT 1 CONCLUDED. 0 CITATIONS. 0 WARNINGS. CONTINUE TO NEXT SHIFT."
```

